variables.name: displayId
variables.comment: * The display id the window is on.

variables.name: bounds
variables.comment: * The window's position and size in display space.

variables.name: isTrustedOverlay
variables.comment: * True if the window is a trusted overlay.

variables.name: isVisible
variables.comment: * True if the window is visible.

variables.name: transform
variables.comment: * Return the transform to get the bounds from display space into window space.

variables.name: isTouchable
variables.comment: * True if the window is touchable.

variables.name: isFocusable
variables.comment: * True if the window is focusable.

variables.name: isPreventSplitting
variables.comment: * True if the window is preventing splitting

variables.name: isDuplicateTouchToWallpaper
variables.comment: * True if the window duplicates touches received to wallpaper.

variables.name: isWatchOutsideTouch
variables.comment:
* True if the window is listening for when there is a touch DOWN event
         * occurring outside its touchable bounds. When such an event occurs,
         * this window will receive a MotionEvent with ACTION_OUTSIDE.
